milestones.description: This is the highest match aggregate (654) involving teams West Indies & U.A.E. in ODIs
Shaiman Anwar and Rameez Shahzad's 140-run partnership is UAE's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 86 between Khurram Khan and Amjad Ali
Rameez Shahzad and Adnan Mufti's 78-run partnership is UAE's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 75 between Rameez Shahzad and Adnan Mufti
Chris Gayle has scored 70 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for WI breaking Brian Lara's record
Shaiman Anwar has broken the record for most sixes (15) in ODIs for UAE, going past Naveed's 12
Rameez Shahzad has scored 2 hundreds in ODIs, the most for UAE breaking Khurram Khan's record
